{
  "stem": "9943.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were even-- actually wanting even to go away somewhere to Australia, or wherever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because it didn't look like there would be any possibility to settle, to find a job, to find work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was-- it didn't look like you can build on something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And at the same time, oh yeah, [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Zonya ?], who, who studied in Germany, he knew what to-- he, he knew more about the anti-Semitism in Germany than I ever would know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I think I'm, I'm going to skip now the rest of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We will just start with the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because there's a lot still to, to be talking about in terms of changes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it came 1939.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the situation got more tense in, in Warsaw [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because of what was going on in Germany.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And you couldn't get a visa to go away someplace.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remember I was interested in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was interested more than [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Zonya ?] because he was an only son.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he could not-- did not feel so simple about-- to, to leave his parents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "His father, as I mentioned, during the year-- I know what I was struggling with.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was going to talk for a few minutes about the role of his father during my life while I was still a student.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because after the second year, we have-- we start clinical work in-- in-- in medicine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The first two years is what is, in this country, pre-med-- chemistry, anatomy, histology-- all this preparatory kind of things for the clinical work.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he liked to have a student in me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So he was really giving me books to read, cases to discuss.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He was a very good teacher.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
